\b Purpose
\b0 \
\
Address Book Pictures is (as it's name states) an application to add images to your Address Book. The current version of Address Book Pictures only uses LDAP servers as a source of images.\
\

\b How To Use
\b0 \
\
The basic process for using Address Book Pictures is:\
\
